Package fr.esiee.baba.model

package fr.esiee.baba.model
  • Class
    Description
    Cellule
    Represents a cell in a grid.
    Direction
    The Direction enum represents the four cardinal directions (UP, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT).
    Element
    The Element enum represents various elements in the game "BABA IS YOU".
    Entity
    The Entity enum represents the different types of entities in the game.
    EntityMove
    Class to manage the movement of entities within the level grid.
    Level
    Manages a single game level in "BABA IS YOU", including the game grid, rules, and game state.
    Noun
    The Noun enum represents various noun elements in the game "BABA IS YOU".
    Operator
    The Operator enum represents the various operators used in "BABA IS YOU" to form gameplay rules.
    Property
    The Property enum represents various properties that elements in the game "BABA IS YOU" can possess.
    Rules
    Manages and evaluates the rules that dictate the interactions and behaviors of elements within the level in "BABA IS YOU".
    Transmutation
    Manages the dynamic effects of rule interactions within the game level, such as melting, defeat, and transformations.
    Word
    The Word class encapsulates the concept of words used in the game "BABA IS YOU", which can be either a noun, an operator, or a property.
